  "commentary": "With SPX at 6825.8 sitting right between the GEX flip at 6808 and the massive +166.9B gamma wall at 6830, dealers are in active hedging mode as spot approaches maximum positive gamma. The PIN regime suggests dealers will aggressively sell into any push toward 6830, creating strong resistance, while the wall break event indicates we've just breached a key level with dealers now scrambling to rehedge positions. Watch 6830 as the critical resistance where dealer selling intensifies, and 6808 as the key support where regime dynamics shift if breached.\n\nBottom line: expect price to get pinned between 6808-6830 with strong resistance at the upper bound.",
